<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f0f4f8;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}

.container {
    text-align: center;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 100px;
    color: #ff6f61;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

a.btn {
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background-color: #ff6f61;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

a.btn:hover {
    background-color: #ff4d40;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
        font-size: 70px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
    }
}
    </style>    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Oops!</h1>
            <p>Looks like you're lost. The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
            <a href="/" class="btn">Go Back Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>